'''Jesesi Mungoshi''' (nanone '''''Jesese Mungoshi''''' ) numukinnyi wa filimi muri [[Zimbabwe]]. Yagaragaye bwa mbere mu 1989, muri filime yitwa, ''Urugendo nyafurika'' . <ref name="AJ">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt0297706/?ref_=m_nm_knf_act_i6</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu kugaragara hakiri kare, Mungoshi yagaragaye muri verisiyo yo mu 1989 ndetse no mu 1990 yakurikiyeho ibice bibiri bya filime y’umuryango wa televiziyo ya George Bloomfield, ''Urugendo nyafurika'', nayo yakinnye: Jason Blicker, Katja Blomquist, Allan Jordan, Ulla Mahaka n'abandi. 

Mu 1991, yagaragaye muri filime ya Godwin Mawuru yise ''Neria'', aho yakinnye nka "Neria". Abandi bakinnyi ni Dominic Kanaveli na Violet Ndlovu mubandi. <ref name="Ner">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt0107670/?ref_=m_nm_knf_i1</ref> <ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/neria/</ref>

Yagaragaye kandi muri filime ngufi ya 1993 na Farai Sevenzo yise, ''Rwendo'', yakinnye na Yemi Ajibade, Ben Daniels, Eldinah Tshatedi na Frank Windsor . <ref name="Rwe">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt0981077/?ref_=m_nm_knf_act_i2</ref>

Muri 2017, yagaragaye muri filime isetsa-y'urukundo, ''Cook Off'', iyobowe na [[Tomas Brickhill]], aho yakinnye nka "Gogo". <ref name="CO">https://m.imdb.com/title/tt7981318/?ref_=m_nm_knf_i3</ref> <ref>https://www.stylist.co.uk/life/netflix-cook-off-film-review-plot-cast-true-story-movie-news/395241</ref> <ref>https://www.newframe.com/film-review-cook-off/</ref> <ref>https://www.newzimbabwe.com/durban-rising-star-tendai-chitima-and-veteran-jesesi-mungoshi-in-zims-first-post-mugabe-film/</ref> Iyi filime ikaba yarakozwe bwa mbere muri Zimbabwe nyuma y’ubutegetsi burebure bwa Robert Mugabe, yerekanwe bwa mbere mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] ku ya 27 Nyakanga 2019. <ref>https://bulawayo24.com/index-id-news-sc-national-byo-166840.html</ref>

Mu rwego rwo gushimira uruhare rwe mu nganda za firime Zimbabwe, yahawe igihembo cya Lifetime Achievement Award na Kaminuza Nkuru ya Zimbabwe muri Gicurasi 2017 i Masvingo . <ref>https://www.newsday.co.zw/2017/05/gzu-honours-jesesi-mungoshi/</ref>

Filime ya 2020, ''Shaina'', aho afatanije nabandi bakinnyi ba Zimbabwe nka: Marian Kunonga, Charmaine Mujeri nabandi bagaragaye, bakiriwe neza mumahanga. <ref name="Sha">https://www.newzimbabwe.com/us-embassy-praises-zimbabwe-film-production-shaina/</ref> <ref>https://www.usaid.gov/zimbabwe/press-releases/new-movie-%E2%80%9Cshaina%E2%80%9D-delivers-powerful-health-messages</ref> <ref>https://nextvafrica.com/ztv-to-air-new-movie-shaina-in-zimbabwe/</ref> <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202008210268.html</ref>

