== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yashakanye n'umwanditsi, umukinnyi n'umusizi wa Zimbabwe, Charles Mungoshi, nk'uko ikinyamakuru ''The Zimbabwe Mail'' na ''Uyu ari'' abanyamakuru bo muri Afurika, yapfuye ku ya 16 Gashyantare 2019 i [[Harare]], muri [[Zimbabwe]] nyuma y'uburwayi yari amaze imyaka 10 afite imyaka 71. Ubukwe bwahiriwe n’abana batanu: Farai, Graham, Nyasha, Charles, na Tsitsi, kandi igihe yapfaga bari bafite abuzukuru barindwi. <ref>https://www.thezimbabwemail.com/zimbabwe/author-and-actor-charles-mungoshi-dead-at-71-family-announces/</ref> <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201902190044.html</ref> Abashakanye bari kumwe numuhungu wabo, Farai bose bari gukina film. <ref>https://nehandaradio.com/2015/10/12/charles-mungoshi-does-the-big-screen/</ref>

